Title: Interdimensional Cable 2: Tempting Fate
Writer: Justin Roiland (created by), Dan Harmon (created by), Dan Guterman, Ryan Ridley, Justin Roiland, Mike McMahan (story editor), David Phillips (story editor), Matt Roller (story editor), Brian Wysol (story editor), Eric Acosta (staff writer), Rich Fulcher (staff writer), Abed Gheith (staff writer), Rashad Gheith (staff writer), Tom Kauffman (staff writer), Wade Randolph (staff writer)
